  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.poster.avif?t=1672145941\" width=650 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.webm?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.mp4?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A STORY TO BE TOLD AND A WORLD TO BE DISCOVERED</strong></h2><br>After waking up not knowing what happened a lioness cub tries to find her owners with the tracks that they left behind not knowing that it will lead her to a journey that will challenge her and know what happened to her owners. Discover the land of Flihela that is filled with windy plains, crimson red forest and snowy ravines all through the eyes of a lioness cub, and a little girl who just lost her precious furry friend blaming herself for what happened. You as the player will take on this journey with the lioness cub also followed by a mysterious bird, to know what happened to the family and where are they.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.poster.avif?t=1672145941\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.webm?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.mp4?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SAVE THAT IS FROZEN FROM TIME</strong></h2><br>Bring back the creatures of Flihela from these mysterious shrines.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/5bddeb90e3f39b531b80cc6fbb90aab9.poster.avif?t=1672145941\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/5bddeb90e3f39b531b80cc6fbb90aab9.webm?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/5bddeb90e3f39b531b80cc6fbb90aab9.mp4?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FRAGMENTS OF TIME</strong></h2><br>Pick up the fragments of time that will show you the past.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.poster.avif?t=1672145941\" width=650 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.webm?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/ef9da3656c70bb1c59b8b222a20b7a86.mp4?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A STORY TO BE TOLD AND A WORLD TO BE DISCOVERED</strong></h2><br>After waking up not knowing what happened a lioness cub tries to find her owners with the tracks that they left behind not knowing that it will lead her to a journey that will challenge her and know what happened to her owners. Discover the land of Flihela that is filled with windy plains, crimson red forest and snowy ravines all through the eyes of a lioness cub, and a little girl who just lost her precious furry friend blaming herself for what happened. You as the player will take on this journey with the lioness cub also followed by a mysterious bird, to know what happened to the family and where are they.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.poster.avif?t=1672145941\" width=650 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.webm?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1518870/extras/48ece28cdcf144d57180d0deae19e011.mp4?t=1672145941\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >